WEBVTT

00:01.462 --> 00:02.543
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:02.543 --> 00:03.754
I START CHEMO TONIGHT.
IT'S LYMPHOMA.

00:03.754 --> 00:05.426
HOW'S YOUR DAUGHTER
TAKING IT?

00:05.426 --> 00:06.627
YOU HAVEN'T TOLD HER.

00:06.627 --> 00:09.050
Nolan: I'VE NEVER MET ANYONE
LIKE YOU.

00:09.050 --> 00:10.341
I'M LEAVING.
 WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

00:10.341 --> 00:12.012
LOS ANGELES.
 HAVE YOU TALKED TO EMILY?

00:12.012 --> 00:13.264
SHE LOVES YOU.

00:13.264 --> 00:14.725
I TOLD HER
I WOULDN'T WAIT.

00:14.725 --> 00:17.058
THE ONLY THING STOPPING YOU
FROM CHOOSING JACK IS YOU.

00:17.058 --> 00:18.639
I DON'T DESERVE HIM!

00:18.639 --> 00:20.191
BUT YOU DESERVE ME?
 BEN, I'M SORRY.

00:20.191 --> 00:22.353
JACK'S FLIGHT LEAVES
IN 20 MINUTES.

00:24.525 --> 00:27.068
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE, MASON?
WE HAD A DEAL.

00:27.068 --> 00:28.109
YES, WE DID.

00:28.109 --> 00:29.990
EVERYTHING CHANGED.
 EVERYTHING BUT YOU.

00:29.990 --> 00:33.534
Louise:
I CAN'T GET AHOLD OF VICTORIA,
AND I'M WORRIED ABOUT HER.

00:33.534 --> 00:35.416
SOMETHING IS NOT RIGHT
WITH HER.

00:35.416 --> 00:37.328
MRS. GRAYSON,
WHAT DO YOU PLAN TO DO?

00:37.328 --> 00:38.369
SOMETHING
AMANDA CLARKE

00:38.369 --> 00:40.371
NEVER HAD THE COURAGE
TO DO HERSELF --

00:40.371 --> 00:41.922
END THIS.
 [ GAS HISSING ]

00:46.377 --> 00:48.379
[ FIRE CRACKLING ]

00:55.176 --> 00:57.178
[ RADIO CHATTER ]

00:57.178 --> 01:00.271
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

01:00.271 --> 01:02.683
[ PANTING ]

01:02.683 --> 01:04.685
THIS AREA IS OFF LIMITS,
MA'AM.

01:06.447 --> 01:08.109
[ SIGHS ]
 David: AMANDA!

01:08.109 --> 01:10.821
AMANDA, OH.
THANK GOD YOU'RE OKAY.

01:10.821 --> 01:12.193
I JUST GOT HOME.
I SAW THE FLAMES.

01:12.193 --> 01:13.404
I WAS SO WORRIED ABOUT YOU.
 I'M FINE.

01:13.404 --> 01:14.995
I'M FINE.

01:14.995 --> 01:16.577
I JUST
CAN'T BELIEVE THIS.

01:19.290 --> 01:22.543
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?!

01:22.543 --> 01:23.754
WELL, TOO SOON TO TELL,
MS. CLARKE.

01:23.754 --> 01:25.876
THINK IT WAS ARSON?
 ANYTHING'S POSSIBLE.

01:25.876 --> 01:27.918
INVESTIGATORS WILL BE ON SITE
WITHIN THE HOUR.

01:27.918 --> 01:30.711
ANYONE ELSE HOME AT THE TIME?
A HOUSEKEEPER, A FRIEND?

01:30.711 --> 01:32.763
NO, THANK GOD.
THE HOUSE IS EMPTY.

01:32.763 --> 01:36.217
I'M VERY SORRY FOR THE LOSS,
MA'AM. PARDON ME.

01:38.639 --> 01:41.522
ALL THESE YEARS, I THOUGHT
ABOUT WATCHING IT BURN.

01:41.522 --> 01:45.686
I NEVER IMAGINED
IT WOULD BE MINE WHEN IT DID.

01:45.686 --> 01:48.489
THERE'S NOTHING ELSE
YOU CAN DO HERE TONIGHT.

01:48.489 --> 01:50.531
LET'S JUST HOPE
THAT IT WAS AN ACCIDENT.

01:51.992 --> 01:54.865
YOU STAY WITH ME NOW.
COME ON, AMANDA.

01:54.865 --> 01:57.238
LET'S GO HOME.

01:57.238 --> 01:59.240
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]

02:01.582 --> 02:03.584
YEAH.

02:10.511 --> 02:12.513
[ SEA GULLS CRYING ]

02:14.805 --> 02:16.177
MORNING, SLEEPYHEAD.

02:16.177 --> 02:19.220
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]
MORNING.

02:19.220 --> 02:20.561
WHAT'S ALL THIS?

02:20.561 --> 02:21.972
WELL, I WAS UP EARLY.

02:21.972 --> 02:24.355
FIGURED I'D SCRAMBLE YOU
A FEW EGGS.

02:24.355 --> 02:25.566
NO BIG DEAL.

02:25.566 --> 02:28.108
WELL,
YOU SHOULD BE CAREFUL.

02:28.108 --> 02:29.530
A GUY COULD
GET USED TO THIS,

02:29.530 --> 02:32.112
AND A GUY COULD REALLY
GET USED TO LAST NIGHT.

02:32.112 --> 02:34.485
[ CHUCKLES ]
IS THAT SO?

02:34.485 --> 02:36.076
MM-HMM.

02:36.076 --> 02:38.909
YOU KNOW...
HEALTHY BREAKFAST,

02:38.909 --> 02:40.621
IT'S, UH -- IT'S JUST ONE WAY
TO START THE DAY.

02:40.621 --> 02:42.082
I, UM...

02:42.082 --> 02:44.955
I CAN THINK OF A FEW OTHERS.
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:44.955 --> 02:47.748
I LOVE THAT IDEA, BUT THIS
WILL HAVE TO SUFFICE.

02:47.748 --> 02:50.050
SOME OF US HAVE TO GET READY
FOR WORK.

02:50.050 --> 02:52.002
BUZZKILL.

02:52.002 --> 02:55.135
WELL, CAN'T BLAME A GUY
FOR TRYING.

02:55.135 --> 02:57.137
BON APPÃ©TIT.
 MM.

03:04.225 --> 03:06.647
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:06.647 --> 03:07.688
[ CLICK ]

03:07.688 --> 03:09.230
[ SIGHS ]

03:09.230 --> 03:12.403
GEEZ, EMS,
WHAT'S WITH ALL THE...

03:15.406 --> 03:17.408
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

03:17.408 --> 03:20.411
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

03:20.411 --> 03:22.032
LOUISE?

03:22.032 --> 03:24.915
DID YOU HEAR ABOUT THE FIRE
AT GRAYSON MANOR?

03:24.915 --> 03:26.086
OF COURSE.

03:26.086 --> 03:28.088
WELL, TELL ME
I SHOULDN'T BE WORRIED.

03:28.088 --> 03:30.381
ABOUT WHAT?
 I TRIED CALLING

03:30.381 --> 03:33.424
VICTORIA SEVERAL TIMES,
BUT SHE HASN'T ANSWERED.

03:33.424 --> 03:36.006
HOW ODD. SHE PROMISED
SHE WOULD CALL ME TODAY.

03:36.006 --> 03:39.219
BUT I STILL HAVEN'T HEARD
FROM HER, EITHER.

03:39.219 --> 03:42.052
WELL, WE BOTH KNOW
SHE HASN'T BEEN HERSELF LATELY.

03:42.052 --> 03:44.845
AND WITH EVERYTHING
THAT EMILY'S DONE TO HER...

03:44.845 --> 03:46.146
[ HORN HONKS IN DISTANCE ]

03:46.146 --> 03:49.109
YOU DON'T THINK SHE HAD ANYTHING
TO DO WITH THAT FIRE, DO YOU?

03:49.109 --> 03:52.022
NO.
DON'T BE RIDICULOUS.

03:52.022 --> 03:54.905
THAT WAS NOTHING MORE THAN KARMA
CATCHING UP WITH EMILY.

03:54.905 --> 03:56.857
IT'S ABOUT TIME.

03:56.857 --> 04:00.120
AS FOR VICTORIA, IF I HAVEN'T
HEARD FROM HER BY LUNCH,

04:00.120 --> 04:03.163
I'LL GO TO THE PENTHOUSE
AND MAKE SURE SHE'S OKAY.

04:08.289 --> 04:10.130
WHAT IS THAT?

04:10.130 --> 04:13.874
I DON'T KNOW, BUT IT'S
VICTORIA'S HANDWRITING.

04:13.874 --> 04:16.677
Nolan: OH, WOW.

04:16.677 --> 04:20.050
AND THE LANDSCAPE
OF THE HAMPTONS WILL
NEVER BE THE SAME.

04:20.050 --> 04:21.802
THAT WAS ALWAYS
OUR GOAL.

04:21.802 --> 04:25.386
HOW CAN YOU NOT BE
A LITTLE UPSET BY THIS?

04:25.386 --> 04:26.807
THIS IS YOUR HOME.

04:26.807 --> 04:29.390
[ SIGHS ] THIS HOUSE
BELONGED TO EMILY THORNE,

04:29.390 --> 04:31.021
NOT AMANDA CLARKE.

04:31.021 --> 04:34.154
AND IT WAS NEVER A HOME.
IT WAS PART OF A PLAN.

04:34.154 --> 04:36.947
YEAH, A PLAN THAT ALMOST BLEW UP
IN YOUR FACE, LITERALLY.

04:36.947 --> 04:39.950
THANK GOD THAT YOU WENT
TO GO STOP JACK,

04:39.950 --> 04:42.533
AND I'M GUESSING
FROM HIS ABSENCE

04:42.533 --> 04:44.114
THAT ONE OF TWO THINGS
HAPPENED.

04:44.114 --> 04:47.748
I WAS TOO LATE.

04:47.748 --> 04:49.960
I'M SO GLAD
IT WAS DOOR NUMBER ONE.

04:49.960 --> 04:51.962
THAT -- T-THAT MEANS
THAT YOU CAN TALK TO HIM

04:51.962 --> 04:53.083
AND TELL HIM
HOW YOU REALLY FEEL,

04:53.083 --> 04:55.466
AND IF EVER
THERE WAS A SIGN FROM GOD

04:55.466 --> 04:56.757
TO BE FREE
AND MOVE ON --

04:56.757 --> 05:00.130
I CAN'T. NOT YET.

05:00.130 --> 05:04.805
I MAY HAVE MISSED JACK,
BUT...I RAN INTO AN OLD FRIEND.

05:04.805 --> 05:07.688
RATHER HE RAN INTO ME.

05:07.688 --> 05:09.560
MASON TREADWELL.

05:09.560 --> 05:10.981
WHAT?

05:10.981 --> 05:13.604
[ SIGHS ]
 CRAZY CAPOTE IS BACK.

05:13.604 --> 05:17.237
I THOUGHT YOU HAD EXILED HIM
TO THE MALDIVES.

05:17.237 --> 05:20.651
CAN'T ANYBODY FOLLOW
A SIMPLE REVENGE PLAN?

05:20.651 --> 05:22.072
OH, RIGHT.

05:22.072 --> 05:24.995
YOU DIDN'T WHEN YOU
REVEALED YOURSELF AS AMANDA.

05:24.995 --> 05:26.997
HE WAS FURIOUS
THAT I BACKED OUT OF OUR DEAL

05:26.997 --> 05:29.159
FOR HIM TO WRITE MY STORY.
 [ SCOFFS ]

05:29.159 --> 05:32.212
WELL,
WHAT DOES HE WANT NOW?

05:32.212 --> 05:34.004
FOR YOU TO GIVE HIM
THE OLD DAVID CLARKE?

05:34.004 --> 05:37.167
CLEAR HIS NAME
SO HE CAN RESURRECT HIMSELF?

05:37.167 --> 05:38.459
I WAS CALLED
ABOUT THE FIRE

05:38.459 --> 05:42.463
BEFORE I COULD EXPLAIN TO HIM
THAT THAT CAN'T HAPPEN.

05:42.463 --> 05:45.095
BUT I'M MEETING WITH HIM TODAY
TO SHUT HIM DOWN.

05:45.095 --> 05:47.267
Man:
WE'VE GOT A BODY OVER HERE!

05:47.267 --> 05:48.308
WHAT?

05:50.100 --> 05:51.181
Victoria:
 "MY DEAREST MARGAUX,

05:51.181 --> 05:54.354
I WRITE TO YOU TODAY
FILLED WITH SADNESS.

05:54.354 --> 05:57.568
AND I'M AFRAID I WILL BE
PASSING THAT SORROW ONTO YOU.

05:57.568 --> 05:59.570
FOR THAT, I AM SORRY.

05:59.570 --> 06:02.653
BUT AS I NOW FIND MY NAME
SYNONYMOUS WITH HATRED,

06:02.653 --> 06:05.035
IT'S AN IDENTITY
I CAN NO LONGER BEAR.

06:05.035 --> 06:09.289
I'VE LOST THE WILL TO FIGHT,
AS THE PAIN RUNS TOO DEEP.

06:09.289 --> 06:11.121
I'M AFRAID THAT LEAVES
ONLY ONE OPTION

06:11.121 --> 06:13.123
THAT MAY SEEM DRASTIC TO YOU.

06:13.123 --> 06:15.335
BODY'S TOO BADLY BURNED
TO IDENTIFY.

06:15.335 --> 06:17.127
BUT WE FOUND THIS
NEAR THE DECEASED.

06:18.879 --> 06:21.261
ANY IDEA
WHO IT BELONGS TO?

06:24.054 --> 06:26.056
I'VE DECIDED TO END MY LIFE.

06:26.056 --> 06:31.271
KNOW THAT MY HEART IS FULL OF
LOVE FOR YOU NOW AND FOREVER.

06:31.271 --> 06:32.853
ETERNALLY YOURS..."

06:32.853 --> 06:35.436
VICTORIA GRAYSON.

06:53.454 --> 06:56.837
SO,
WHAT CAUSED THE FIRE?

06:56.837 --> 07:00.040
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]
I DON'T KNOW YET, BUT...

07:00.040 --> 07:02.923
WHAT?

07:02.923 --> 07:05.135
[ SIGHS ]

07:05.135 --> 07:07.217
THEY FOUND A BODY
IN THE DEBRIS.

07:08.969 --> 07:10.010
[ SCOFFS ]

07:10.010 --> 07:13.433
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I'M ABOUT TO SAY THIS, BUT...

07:13.433 --> 07:15.816
THEY THINK IT
MIGHT HAVE BEEN VICTORIA.

07:15.816 --> 07:17.728
THE CORONER'S TRYING
TO CONFIRM RIGHT NOW.

07:17.728 --> 07:19.730
THAT CAN'T BE.

07:19.730 --> 07:21.942
I KNOW.

07:21.942 --> 07:25.826
THEY FOUND THE ENGAGEMENT RING
PASCAL GAVE HER, BUT...

07:25.826 --> 07:27.067
WHAT IF
SHE PLANTED IT THERE

07:27.067 --> 07:29.159
TO MAKE IT LOOK LIKE
SOMEONE KILLED HER?

07:29.159 --> 07:30.991
THAT'S CERTAINLY IN LINE WITH
SOMETHING VICTORIA WOULD DO.

07:30.991 --> 07:32.833
I MEAN, THIS WHOLE THING
COULD BE A HOAX.

07:32.833 --> 07:34.164
Ben: BUT IT'S NOT.

07:34.164 --> 07:35.786
THE REMAINS WERE TOO BURNT
FOR DNA,

07:35.786 --> 07:38.128
SO ALL WE HAD TO GO ON
WERE THE TEETH WE RECOVERED.

07:38.128 --> 07:40.921
BUT THE CORONER CHECKED
HER DENTAL RECORDS.

07:40.921 --> 07:42.753
IT'S DEFINITELY
VICTORIA GRAYSON.

07:42.753 --> 07:45.926
[ SIGHS ]

07:45.926 --> 07:48.138
[ SCOFFS ]

07:48.138 --> 07:52.012
AFTER...ALL THE YEARS OF PAIN
THAT SHE'S CAUSED OUR FAMILY.

07:52.012 --> 07:54.054
[ SCOFFS ]

07:54.054 --> 07:57.858
AND SHE TRIED TO CAUSE MORE
BY KILLING ME.

07:57.858 --> 07:58.979
AND FAILED.

07:58.979 --> 08:00.270
ACTUALLY, YOU'RE WRONG.

08:00.270 --> 08:02.482
WE GOT A CALL
FROM MARGAUX LeMARCHAL.

08:02.482 --> 08:04.695
VICTORIA LEFT A SUICIDE NOTE.

08:07.237 --> 08:08.448
[ SIGHS ]

08:08.448 --> 08:11.451
SHE WANTED TO DIE
IN GRAYSON MANOR.

08:11.451 --> 08:13.453
YEAH,
THAT HOUSE WAS A SYMBOL

08:13.453 --> 08:15.996
OF EVERYTHING THE GRAYSON NAME
STOOD FOR --

08:15.996 --> 08:18.579
WEALTH, POWER, STATUS.

08:18.579 --> 08:21.001
SHE SIMPLY WANTED TO DIE
IN THE PLACE SHE CHERISHED MOST.

08:21.001 --> 08:23.423
AND TO TAKE BACK
WHAT I HAD TAKEN FROM HER.

08:23.423 --> 08:26.086
I'M HERE BECAUSE
I HAVE ONE QUESTION.

08:26.086 --> 08:27.427
HOW DID SHE BYPASS
YOUR SECURITY?

08:29.009 --> 08:31.221
I'VE SEEN BEHIND THE CURTAIN,
REMEMBER?

08:31.221 --> 08:33.804
SO HAS SHE.

08:33.804 --> 08:36.395
SHE MANAGED TO STEAL
SOME INFORMATION FROM US.

08:36.395 --> 08:37.808
NOLAN'S SPECS
ON MY ALARM

08:37.808 --> 08:40.059
MUST HAVE BEEN
AMONG THE THINGS SHE GOT.

08:40.059 --> 08:43.984
WELL, AT LEAST THIS WAR'S OVER
BETWEEN YOU TWO.

08:43.984 --> 08:47.407
I'LL BE IN TOUCH
IF WE HAVE ANY FOLLOW-UP.

08:47.407 --> 08:49.820
UH, THANKS
FOR LETTING US KNOW.

08:49.820 --> 08:52.492
I REALLY APPRECIATE --

08:52.492 --> 08:54.865
I WAS JUST DOING MY JOB.

08:54.865 --> 08:56.917
I WAS DISPATCHED TO THE SCENE.
THAT'S ALL.

08:56.917 --> 08:59.710
[ SIGHS ]

08:59.710 --> 09:01.371
BEN, IT DOESN'T
NEED TO BE LIKE THIS.

09:01.371 --> 09:05.005
DOESN'T IT?
YOU MADE YOUR CHOICE.

09:13.343 --> 09:16.136
[ CHUCKLES ]
OH, I LIKE THAT.

09:16.136 --> 09:19.139
YOU HAVE TO BUILD
THAT ONE TALLER. GOOD JOB.

09:19.139 --> 09:21.602
YOU KNOW, I WAS JUST THINKING
ABOUT HOW GREAT IT'LL BE

09:21.602 --> 09:23.984
TO DO THIS
IN THE MIDDLE OF WINTER.

09:23.984 --> 09:27.858
NOT THAT I WON'T HAVE MY OWN
LESS IMPRESSIVE PLACE BY THEN.

09:27.858 --> 09:30.150
[ CHUCKLES ] YOU KNOW YOU
CAN STAY AS LONG AS YOU WANT.

09:30.150 --> 09:32.993
CAREFUL WHAT YOU OFFER.
I JUST MIGHT TAKE YOU UP ON IT.

09:32.993 --> 09:34.785
OH, I'M COUNTING ON IT.

09:34.785 --> 09:38.118
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
I HAVE YOU BOTH OUT HERE.

09:38.118 --> 09:40.000
AFTER I TRIED TO CONVINCE
YOU LAST YEAR,

09:40.000 --> 09:41.081
I HAD TO
RECONCILE MYSELF

09:41.081 --> 09:43.253
TO THE FACT
THAT IT WOULD NEVER HAPPEN.

09:43.253 --> 09:45.465
[ LIQUID POURS ]

09:45.465 --> 09:47.007
JACK,
I'M SO PROUD OF YOU.

09:48.298 --> 09:51.802
I'M GLAD YOU DECIDED
TO PUT THE PAST BEHIND YOU.

09:53.844 --> 09:56.847
YEAH, IT JUST FEELS RIGHT,
YOU KNOW?

09:56.847 --> 09:59.099
FRESH START'S
EXACTLY WHAT WE NEEDED.

09:59.099 --> 10:00.480
NOW I'M JUST GONNA
HAVE TO COMPETE WITH ACTORS

10:00.480 --> 10:03.223
FOR BARTENDING JOBS.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

10:03.223 --> 10:05.856
AT LEAST UNTIL I GET
ON MY OWN FEET AGAIN, YOU KNOW?

10:05.856 --> 10:08.438
[ TABLET CHIMES ]

10:08.438 --> 10:10.110
[ SIGHS, SNIFFS ]
HEY, BUDDY.

10:10.110 --> 10:11.992
JACK, YOU'RE GONNA
WANT TO SEE THIS.

10:14.154 --> 10:16.536
Woman: ...HERE AMID THE RUBBLE
FROM LAST NIGHT'S BLAZE

10:16.536 --> 10:18.739
AT WHAT WAS KNOWN
AS GRAYSON MANOR.

10:18.739 --> 10:21.161
EAST COAST SOCIETY CIRCLES
ARE ABUZZ THIS MORNING

10:21.161 --> 10:23.954
WITH NEWS THAT HAMPTON
SOCIALITE VICTORIA GRAYSON

10:23.954 --> 10:26.086
WAS A CASUALTY
IN THE DEADLY EXPLOSION.

10:26.086 --> 10:28.088
OH, MY GOD.
 THE HOUSE BELONGED TO
THE GRAYSON FAMILY

10:28.088 --> 10:29.299
FOR MORE THAN TWO DECADES

10:29.299 --> 10:31.091
BEFORE BEING PURCHASED
BY EMILY THORNE,

10:31.091 --> 10:34.214
WHO JUST LAST WEEK REVEALED
HERSELF TO BE AMANDA CLARKE.

10:34.214 --> 10:37.217
THERE WAS A LONG HISTORY OF
TRAGEDY, HEARTACHE, AND SCANDAL

10:37.217 --> 10:38.258
AMONG THESE RUINS.

10:38.258 --> 10:40.350
JUST SIX WEEKS AGO,
DANIEL GRAYSON...

10:40.350 --> 10:41.762
[ BIRDS CHIRPING ]

10:41.762 --> 10:44.935
I THOUGHT YOU'D WANT TO KNOW
RIGHT AWAY.

10:44.935 --> 10:47.147
DING DONG,
THE BITCH IS DEAD.

10:47.147 --> 10:48.318
[ SIGHS ]

10:48.318 --> 10:50.941
VICTORIA GRAYSON HAS ACTUALLY
TAKEN HER LAST BREATH.

10:50.941 --> 10:52.072
HMM.

10:52.072 --> 10:53.653
[ SCOFFS ]

10:53.653 --> 10:56.867
IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE,
BUT...

10:56.867 --> 10:58.238
CORONER CONFIRMED IT.

10:58.238 --> 11:00.580
AND SHE LIT THE MATCH
HERSELF?

11:00.580 --> 11:03.333
I GOT TO SAY
I DID NOT SEE THAT COMING.

11:03.333 --> 11:07.167
A GUILTY CONSCIENCE
CAN BE A POWERFUL THING.

11:10.841 --> 11:12.843
SO...

11:12.843 --> 11:17.057
WHAT DOES THE WORLD SANS
VICTORIA GRAYSON EVEN LOOK LIKE?

11:17.057 --> 11:18.638
REVENGE-FREE.

11:18.638 --> 11:20.260
AND I DIDN'T EVEN
HAVE TO SNAP HER NECK.

11:20.260 --> 11:23.063
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:23.063 --> 11:25.896
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU DIDN'T HEAR THE EXPLOSION.

11:25.896 --> 11:30.650
WELL, I WAS ENTERTAINING...
A GUEST.

11:30.650 --> 11:31.651
[ SIGHS ]

11:31.651 --> 11:34.234
WE WERE MAKING
OUR OWN NOISE.

11:34.234 --> 11:35.866
TONY?

11:35.866 --> 11:38.238
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:38.238 --> 11:40.660
EMILY, I THINK...

11:40.660 --> 11:41.992
I THINK I'M FALLING
FOR HIM.

11:41.992 --> 11:44.785
I KNOW. I KNOW.

11:44.785 --> 11:48.168
WHAT WOULD YOU SAY IF
I ASKED HIM ON A LITTLE VACAY?

11:48.168 --> 11:51.171
SOMEWHERE FAR
FROM THE HAMPTONS.

11:51.171 --> 11:53.423
TOO SOON?
 NO, I'D SAY GO FOR IT.

11:53.423 --> 11:56.006
DON'T HOLD BACK,
NOLAN.

11:56.006 --> 11:58.218
THAT'S WHAT I DID WITH JACK,
AND LOOK WHERE IT GOT ME.

11:58.218 --> 12:02.512
AND I HAVE A PRIVATE JET
AT YOUR BECK AND CALL...

12:02.512 --> 12:04.344
IF YOU WANT TO FIX THAT.

12:04.344 --> 12:07.727
AND I WILL.

12:07.727 --> 12:09.519
BUT FIRST I HAVE TO DEAL
WITH MASON,

12:09.519 --> 12:12.522
AND KNOWING HIM, I'M PROBABLY
GONNA NEED YOUR HELP...

12:12.522 --> 12:16.116
HMM.
 ...SO DON'T PACK YOUR BAGS
JUST YET.

12:41.681 --> 12:43.303
[ SNEEZES, GRUNTS ]

12:43.303 --> 12:45.145
[ SNIFFS, SIGHS ]

12:45.145 --> 12:49.099
I HAD TO FLY IN DISGUISE
AND IN ECONOMY TO GET HERE.

12:49.099 --> 12:51.021
[ SNIFFS ]

12:51.021 --> 12:52.813
SIT WITH THE COMMON MAN,
CATCH THE COMMON COLD.

12:52.813 --> 12:54.234
[ SNIFFS ]
I'M NOT HAPPY ABOUT IT,

12:54.234 --> 12:57.487
NOR AM I HAPPY ABOUT
YOUR BEING LATE, MS. CLARKE.

12:57.487 --> 12:59.069
WELL, I HAD A FEW PROBLEMS
TO DEAL WITH.

12:59.069 --> 13:00.991
AH, YES.

13:00.991 --> 13:04.204
YES, I HEARD YOUR HOUSE
WENT UP IN FLAMES.

13:04.204 --> 13:07.577
TRAGIC. GEE,
I WONDER HOW THAT FEELS.

13:07.577 --> 13:10.170
LOOK, MASON --
 THE GOOD NEWS
IS THAT YOUR BIGGEST PROBLEM

13:10.170 --> 13:11.541
DIED IN THAT FIRE,

13:11.541 --> 13:14.124
THOUGH I ALWAYS THOUGHT VICTORIA
WOULD FIRST BURN IN HELL,

13:14.124 --> 13:15.966
NOT IN THE HAMPTONS.

13:15.966 --> 13:19.219
BUT NOW IT'S TIME TO FOCUS
ON ME

13:19.219 --> 13:21.131
AND CLEARING ME
OF KILLING GORDON MURPHY

13:21.131 --> 13:24.134
BEFORE I, TOO,
BECOME A WHITE-HAIRED MAN.

13:24.134 --> 13:25.345
THINGS HAVE CHANGED.

13:25.345 --> 13:26.476
WHEN I MADE
THAT PROMISE,

13:26.476 --> 13:28.058
I WAS PLANNING ON TAKING
THE BLAME FOR YOU

13:28.058 --> 13:29.850
AND RUNNING AWAY
FROM HERE FOREVER.

13:29.850 --> 13:31.811
STILL A GREAT PLAN.

13:31.811 --> 13:33.984
DON'T GIVE UP ON YOURSELF.
[ SNIFFS ]

13:33.984 --> 13:36.196
LOOK, I'M NOT GONNA
PUT MYSELF AT RISK.

13:36.196 --> 13:38.528
MY FATHER IS ALIVE NOW.

13:38.528 --> 13:41.741
I FINALLY HAVE THE CHANCE
TO BE HAPPY, TO...

13:41.741 --> 13:43.994
TRY TO HAVE THE LIFE
I ALWAYS WANTED.

13:43.994 --> 13:48.038
WELL, WHO KNEW THAT A SIDE
EFFECT OF HAPPINESS IS NAIVETY?

13:48.038 --> 13:49.709
I WANT THE LIFE
 I DESERVE.

13:49.709 --> 13:51.121
THEN NAME THE PLACE,
AND I'LL SET IT UP.

13:51.121 --> 13:53.503
I'LL GET YOU A NEW IDENTITY,
EVERYTHING THAT YOU WANT.

13:53.503 --> 13:54.754
HAS AMANDA CLARKE
FORGOTTEN

13:54.754 --> 13:57.167
EMILY THORNE ALREADY DANGLED
THAT RANCID CARROT?

13:57.167 --> 14:00.670
YOU THINK I WAS HAPPY
IN THE MALDIVES?

14:00.670 --> 14:02.802
IT'S SINKING INTO THE OCEAN,
FOR GOD'S SAKE.

14:02.802 --> 14:03.843
OH,
AND HAVE I MENTIONED

14:03.843 --> 14:06.846
THAT WHILE WATER ROSE
ABOVE MY ANKLES,

14:06.846 --> 14:09.019
I STARTED WRITING
ANOTHER TOME?

14:09.019 --> 14:13.433
I'M CALLING IT "ONE BIG LIE:
THE AMANDA CLARKE STORY."

14:13.433 --> 14:16.146
IT'LL BE YOUR WORD
AGAINST MINE.

14:16.146 --> 14:17.187
THINK ABOUT IT.

14:17.187 --> 14:18.979
A BOOK WRITTEN
BY A DEAD MAN.

14:18.979 --> 14:21.031
PEOPLE WILL EAT THAT UP.

14:21.031 --> 14:23.984
IT'S SURE TO BLOW THE LID
OFF THIS GOOD-GIRL IMAGE

14:23.984 --> 14:25.655
YOU TRICKED PEOPLE
INTO BELIEVING.

14:25.655 --> 14:29.079
AT THE VERY LEAST,
IT'LL OPEN UP A POLICE INQUIRY.

14:29.079 --> 14:31.871
IT'LL HAUNT YOU
THE REST OF YOUR DAYS

14:31.871 --> 14:34.874
AND DESTROY WHATEVER
NORMAN ROCKWELL LIFE

14:34.874 --> 14:37.457
YOU THINK YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE
WITH YOUR FATHER.

14:37.457 --> 14:39.089
[ SNIFFS ]

14:39.089 --> 14:41.461
YOU HAVE TWO DAYS
TO CLEAR MY NAME,

14:41.461 --> 14:44.884
OR I SEND THE FIRST 50 PAGES
TO PUBLISHERS,

14:44.884 --> 14:46.676
NEWSPAPERS,
AND HOMELAND SECURITY.

14:46.676 --> 14:47.847
[ SNIFFS ]

14:49.389 --> 14:50.810
YOUR MOVE, AMANDA.

14:59.689 --> 15:01.781
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

15:03.613 --> 15:05.615
[ SIGHS ]

15:05.615 --> 15:06.866
JACKIE BOY.

15:06.866 --> 15:09.449
HEY, UH, THOUGHT I'D GIVE YOU
AT LEAST 24 HOURS

15:09.449 --> 15:11.661
WITHOUT ANY HAMPTONS DRAMA.

15:11.661 --> 15:13.873
IT'S KIND OF HARD TO AVOID
WHEN IT'S ALL OVER THE NEWS.

15:13.873 --> 15:15.085
Don't worry.

15:15.085 --> 15:18.668
ALL THINGS CONSIDERED,
EMS IS DOING OKAY.

15:18.668 --> 15:20.340
I'm not calling
about how she's doing.

15:20.340 --> 15:21.962
I'm calling about
what she did.

15:21.962 --> 15:23.173
[ SIGHS ]

15:23.173 --> 15:25.545
THEY'RE SAYING THAT VICTORIA
COMMITTED SUICIDE.

15:25.545 --> 15:27.257
BUT PLEASE TELL ME
THAT THIS ISN'T JUST

15:27.257 --> 15:29.309
some sort of poetic end
to Emily's revenge plan,

15:29.309 --> 15:30.680
THAT SHE'S NOT
THAT FAR GONE.

15:30.680 --> 15:34.104
NO, OF COURSE NOT.
NO, VICKIE DID HERSELF IN.

15:34.104 --> 15:37.857
AND SHE LEFT A NOTE AND HER
CHOMPERS BEHIND AS EVIDENCE.

15:37.857 --> 15:40.730
BESIDES, YOU KNOW EMS WOULD
NEVER GO DEATH SQUAD ON ANYONE.

15:40.730 --> 15:43.063
I'M NOT SURE
WHAT I KNOW ANYMORE.

15:43.063 --> 15:45.155
[ DOOR OPENS ]

15:45.155 --> 15:47.527
UH, WELL,
OUR FAVORITE EX-REVENGER

15:47.527 --> 15:49.119
JUST WALKED
THROUGH THE DOOR.

15:49.119 --> 15:50.870
WANT ME TO GIVE HER
YOUR REGARDS?

15:50.870 --> 15:54.454
I HAVE TO GO.
I'LL BE IN TOUCH.

15:54.454 --> 15:55.495
[ BEEP ]

15:55.495 --> 15:56.916
[ SCOFFS ]

15:56.916 --> 15:59.539
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

15:59.539 --> 16:03.213
[ SIGHS ]
WAS THAT JACK?

16:03.213 --> 16:05.795
UM...YEAH.
WELL...HE HAD TO RUN.

16:05.795 --> 16:07.467
YOU KNOW,
CARL WAS CRYING.

16:07.467 --> 16:08.758
YOU DON'T HAVE TO LIE,
NOLAN.

16:08.758 --> 16:12.762
I KNOW WHY HE'S ANGRY WITH ME,
AND...I'M GONNA FIX IT.

16:12.762 --> 16:14.354
BUT FIRST,
I NEED YOUR HELP.

16:14.354 --> 16:15.805
MM.

16:15.805 --> 16:18.228
IS THERE ANY WAY TO CREATE SOME
KIND OF PRE-DATED PAPER TRAIL

16:18.228 --> 16:20.060
FROM CONRAD GRAYSON
TO HIS LAWYER?

16:20.060 --> 16:23.063
SOMETHING THAT PROVES THAT
CONRAD KILLED GORDON MURPHY

16:23.063 --> 16:24.444
AND FRAMED MASON FOR IT?

16:24.444 --> 16:27.737
SO, OUR PAL WOULDN'T TAKE NO
FOR AN ANSWER?

16:27.737 --> 16:31.031
WELL, YEAH, I MEAN,

16:31.031 --> 16:32.412
I COULD CREATE A MOUNTAIN
OF PHONY DOCUMENTS,

16:32.412 --> 16:33.993
BUT WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
THE U.S. ATTORNEY'S OFFICE

16:33.993 --> 16:37.037
WOULDN'T BE SLIGHTLY SUSPICIOUS
ABOUT WHERE THEY CAME FROM?

16:37.037 --> 16:40.040
EH, LEAVE THAT TO ME.

16:43.963 --> 16:45.965
CARL'S DOWN FOR HIS NAP.

16:45.965 --> 16:47.967
[ SIGHS ]

16:47.967 --> 16:49.589
THANKS.

16:49.589 --> 16:51.551
QUITE A DAY, HUH?

16:51.551 --> 16:54.764
I STILL CAN'T FATHOM THE IDEA
THAT VICTORIA'S GONE.

16:56.436 --> 17:01.061
THAT WOMAN CHANGED THE COURSE
OF MY LIFE.

17:01.061 --> 17:06.276
SHE STOLE MY HUSBAND.
SHE...DROVE ME TO DRINK.

17:06.276 --> 17:08.318
SHE RAN ME OUT OF TOWN.

17:08.318 --> 17:12.152
YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY PERSON
WHOSE LIFE SHE DESTROYED.

17:12.152 --> 17:12.992
RIGHT.

17:15.115 --> 17:17.287
HOW IS EMILY, ANYWAY?

17:17.287 --> 17:21.621
IS SHE RESPONSIBLE
FOR THIS?

17:23.123 --> 17:25.335
CARL'S BEDROOM
IS RIGHT UPSTAIRS.

17:25.335 --> 17:28.167
I COULDN'T HELP BUT OVERHEAR
YOUR CONVERSATION WITH NOLAN.

17:30.550 --> 17:32.762
HE SAID
THAT HER HANDS ARE CLEAN.

17:32.762 --> 17:34.344
[ SCOFFS ]

17:37.137 --> 17:38.938
WHY DO YOU HAVE TO KNOW?

17:38.938 --> 17:41.060
HUH?

17:41.060 --> 17:45.685
I WORRY THAT EMILY
STILL HAS A HOLD ON YOU.

17:45.685 --> 17:48.108
YOU DON'T HAVE TO.

17:48.108 --> 17:50.069
I'M NOT GOING BACK
TO THE HAMPTONS.

17:50.069 --> 17:51.991
THERE'S NOTHING
FOR ME THERE.

17:53.453 --> 17:56.656
NOT ANYMORE.

17:59.459 --> 18:01.121
Martinez: MRS. GRAYSON
MUST HAVE BEEN

18:01.121 --> 18:03.123
IN A LOT OF PAIN
TO DO SUCH A THING.

18:03.123 --> 18:04.624
TERRIBLE TRAGEDY.

18:04.624 --> 18:07.207
MY CONDOLENCES
ON THE LOSS OF YOUR HOME.

18:07.207 --> 18:09.709
WELL, STRANGELY, THAT'S
WHAT BRINGS ME HERE TODAY.

18:09.709 --> 18:11.131
HOW IS THAT?

18:11.131 --> 18:14.053
I WAS SALVAGING SOME OF
MY BELONGINGS FROM THE WRECKAGE,

18:14.053 --> 18:16.846
AND I STUMBLED UPON...

18:16.846 --> 18:19.849
A HIDDEN COMPARTMENT
IN THE FLOOR OF MY DEN.

18:19.849 --> 18:22.272
I WOULD NEVER HAVE SEEN IT
HAD IT NOT BEEN FOR THE FIRE.

18:22.272 --> 18:25.565
AND INSIDE OF IT...
[ SIGHS ]

18:25.565 --> 18:27.066
...WAS THIS
FIREPROOF BOX...

18:28.358 --> 18:33.112
...FILLED WITH DOCUMENTS
BELONGING TO CONRAD GRAYSON.

18:33.112 --> 18:34.734
THERE'S NO END
TO THAT GUY'S SECRETS.

18:34.734 --> 18:37.537
WELL, I'M NO LAWYER, BUT
IT SEEMS THAT CONRAD WAS UP TO

18:37.537 --> 18:40.200
WAY MORE THAN THIS OFFICE
WAS EVEN AWARE OF.

18:40.200 --> 18:42.742
I FIGURED
YOU'D WANT TO SEE THESE.

18:42.742 --> 18:46.166
THANK YOU, MS. CLARKE.
WE'LL INVESTIGATE FURTHER.

18:46.166 --> 18:48.918
THE D.O.J. TAKES ANYTHING
REGARDING MR. GRAYSON

18:48.918 --> 18:50.920
VERY SERIOUSLY.
 JUST TRYING TO DO MY PART.

18:50.920 --> 18:52.302
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

18:54.384 --> 18:55.595
IT'S DONE.

18:55.595 --> 18:56.806
I'M PLEASED
TO HEAR THAT.

18:56.806 --> 18:58.218
YOU WON'T BE IN HIDING
MUCH LONGER.

18:58.218 --> 18:59.809
THE U.S. ATTORNEY
IS HOLDING PROOF

18:59.809 --> 19:02.021
THAT CONRAD KILLED GORDON MURPHY
AND FRAMED YOU FOR IT.

19:02.021 --> 19:05.064
I SMELL A POSTHUMOUS PARDON,
DON'T YOU?

19:05.064 --> 19:07.026
IN THE MEANTIME,
STAY OUT OF SIGHT.

19:07.026 --> 19:09.899
OH, NOT TO WORRY. I'VE BECOME
A MASTER AT PLAYING DEAD.

19:09.899 --> 19:11.481
I'LL CONTACT YOU
WHEN IT'S TIME

19:11.481 --> 19:12.862
FOR YOUR OFFICIAL
RESURRECTION.

19:12.862 --> 19:15.695
OH, I ANXIOUSLY
AWAIT YOUR CALL.

19:17.827 --> 19:19.989
YOU WERE RIGHT.

19:19.989 --> 19:24.204
BEING HERE IN VICTORIA'S HOME
AROUND HER BELONGINGS,

19:24.204 --> 19:25.995
IT DOES HELP A LITTLE.

19:25.995 --> 19:28.588
HOW DID I MISS THIS?

19:28.588 --> 19:31.791
I KNEW SHE WAS IN A DARK PLACE,
BUT...

19:31.791 --> 19:33.172
THE PAIN
SHE MUST HAVE BEEN IN

19:33.172 --> 19:35.054
TO DO SOMETHING LIKE THAT
TO HERSELF.

19:35.054 --> 19:37.056
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

19:37.056 --> 19:40.600
BESIDES, I'M STILL
NOT ENTIRELY CONVINCED.

19:40.600 --> 19:42.392
I'VE BEEN IN AND OUT
OF MENTAL INSTITUTIONS

19:42.392 --> 19:44.103
FOR MOST OF MY LIFE,

19:44.103 --> 19:46.266
AND I KNOW SUICIDAL TENDENCIES
WHEN I SEE THEM.

19:46.266 --> 19:48.978
SHE DIDN'T SHOW
ANY OF THE USUAL SIGNS.

19:48.978 --> 19:50.400
OH, LOUISE.

19:50.400 --> 19:54.614
IT'S NORMAL TO LOOK FOR ANSWERS
AT A TIME LIKE THIS.

19:54.614 --> 19:58.027
BUT WE READ HER NOTE.

19:58.027 --> 19:59.619
SHE WAS RESOLUTE
IN HER DECISION.

19:59.619 --> 20:00.780
WAS SHE, THOUGH?

20:00.780 --> 20:03.583
I MEAN, I SAW THE DATE BOOK
ON HER DESK,

20:03.583 --> 20:05.995
AND SHE SCHEDULED
A MANI/PEDI FOR NEXT WEEK.

20:05.995 --> 20:07.587
NOW, WHY WOULD SOMEONE
WITH A DEATH WISH

20:07.587 --> 20:09.379
WORRY ABOUT
THEIR CUTICLES?

20:09.379 --> 20:11.130
JUST DOESN'T MAKE
ANY SENSE.

20:11.130 --> 20:14.213
DEATH RARELY DOES.

20:14.213 --> 20:17.216
I'LL GET US A REFILL.

20:25.054 --> 20:27.186
MARGAUX!
COME QUICK!

20:27.186 --> 20:29.479
SOMEONE FORCED
THIS DOOR OPEN.

20:29.479 --> 20:32.692
OH, MY GOD,
THERE IS BLOOD.

20:32.692 --> 20:35.194
I THINK SOMEONE BROKE IN HERE
AND ATTACKED VICTORIA.

20:35.194 --> 20:37.156
WE NEED TO CALL
THE POLICE.

20:37.156 --> 20:38.778
I KNEW IT.

20:38.778 --> 20:40.910
THIS WASN'T A SUICIDE
AT ALL.

20:40.910 --> 20:42.282
[ SCOFFS ]

20:42.282 --> 20:43.783
THIS WAS MURDER.

20:48.918 --> 20:49.919
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

20:49.919 --> 20:51.040
HEY, IS NOLAN HERE?

20:51.040 --> 20:53.002
SHOULD HAVE BEEN HERE
AN HOUR AGO.

20:54.714 --> 20:56.926
YOU MONSTER!

20:56.926 --> 21:01.220
YOU KILLED VICTORIA
ON THE SAME SPOT HER SON DIED.

21:01.220 --> 21:02.302
HOW COULD YOU?

21:02.302 --> 21:03.513
LOUISE,
I KNOW YOU'RE BROKEN UP

21:03.513 --> 21:04.724
AND YOU'RE TRYING
TO PASS THE BLAME,

21:04.724 --> 21:07.096
BUT I HAD NOTHING
TO DO WITH THIS.

21:07.096 --> 21:09.649
VICTORIA'S DEATH WAS RULED
A SUICIDE BY THE POLICE.
IT'S OVER.

21:09.649 --> 21:11.230
OH,
THAT'S YESTERDAY'S NEWS.

21:11.230 --> 21:12.562
NOW THEY'RE
CALLING IT MURDER.

21:12.562 --> 21:14.484
AND WITH MY HELP,
IT'S ONLY A MATTER OF TIME

21:14.484 --> 21:17.777
UNTIL THEY PROVE YOU'RE
THE ONE THAT ATTACKED
HER IN THAT GARAGE.

21:17.777 --> 21:20.740
THIS AGAIN? LET IT GO, LOUISE.
IT WASN'T ME.

21:20.740 --> 21:22.161
BUT THAT WASN'T ENOUGH
FOR YOU, WAS IT?

21:22.161 --> 21:23.533
YOU HAD TO GO AND KILL HER!
 YOU ARE CRAZY.

21:23.533 --> 21:26.536
THIS IS NOTHING BUT FABRICATIONS
AND LIES. I'M LEAVING.

21:26.536 --> 21:27.957
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

21:27.957 --> 21:31.671
HUH, I WONDER
WHO THAT COULD BE.

21:31.671 --> 21:33.753
HAMPTONS' FINEST,
PERHAPS.

21:33.753 --> 21:36.796
NOT AS CRAZY
AS YOU THOUGHT I WAS.

21:36.796 --> 21:39.589
YOU WILL PAY DEARLY
FOR WHAT YOU'VE DONE,

21:39.589 --> 21:42.802
AND I WILL BE THE FIRST
ON THE STAND TO TESTIFY TO IT.

21:53.142 --> 21:55.194
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

21:59.238 --> 22:00.530
HI.

22:00.530 --> 22:04.243
I JUST, UH, GOT CALLED
INTO THE POLICE STATION.

22:04.243 --> 22:09.208
APPARENTLY, VICTORIA'S DEATH
IS NOW CONSIDERED A HOMICIDE.

22:09.208 --> 22:12.001
YEAH,
THEY CALLED ME IN, TOO.

22:12.001 --> 22:14.333
I THINK THEY'RE JUST
COVERING THEIR BASES.

22:18.668 --> 22:20.460
[ LIQUID POURS ]

22:20.460 --> 22:22.672
DAD, IS THEY'RE SOMETHING
YOU'RE NOT TELLING ME?

22:22.672 --> 22:24.263
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

22:24.263 --> 22:27.887
IF THERE IS A REASON
FOR AN INVESTIGATION,

22:27.887 --> 22:29.389
WE ARE
THE PRIME SUSPECTS.

22:30.850 --> 22:35.234
AND I CAN'T HAVE ANYTHING BAD
HAPPEN TO YOU RIGHT NOW.

22:35.234 --> 22:39.068
NOTHING BAD
IS GONNA HAPPEN.

22:39.068 --> 22:40.359
I PROMISE.

22:40.359 --> 22:41.360
[ SIGHS ]

22:41.360 --> 22:43.152
WHERE WERE YOU
LAST NIGHT?

22:43.152 --> 22:46.786
I WAS WORKING
ON MY BOAT.

22:46.786 --> 22:48.117
BY MYSELF.

22:48.117 --> 22:50.750
[ SIGHS ] PLEASE TELL ME
SOMEONE SAW YOU.

22:50.750 --> 22:52.121
A PASSERBY ON THE PIER,
ANYONE?

22:53.453 --> 22:56.045
I BELIEVE YOU,
BUT THE POLICE MIGHT NOT.

22:56.045 --> 22:59.128
I WAS, UH, BELOW DECK FIXING
THE ALTERNATOR THE WHOLE TIME.

23:00.420 --> 23:03.002
COME ON.

23:03.002 --> 23:05.174
LET'S GET GOING.

23:11.350 --> 23:12.972
WOW.

23:14.013 --> 23:17.437
SEEING YOU LIKE THAT,

23:17.437 --> 23:19.439
DEFINITELY THINKING
SOMEWHERE TROPICAL.

23:19.439 --> 23:20.610
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

23:23.022 --> 23:26.826
I'M CONSIDERING TAKING
A MUCH-NEEDED VACATION,

23:26.826 --> 23:29.829
AND...
PIÃA COLADAS FOR TWO

23:29.829 --> 23:32.161
SOUND A LOT MORE EXCITING
THAN PIÃA COLADAS FOR ONE.

23:32.161 --> 23:34.163
REALLY?

23:34.163 --> 23:37.747
I KNOW IT'S CRAZY-FAST FOR US
TO BE TRAVEL MATES.

23:37.747 --> 23:39.669
IT'S ALMOST LIKE I'M ASKING YOU
TO SHACK UP OR SOMETHING,

23:39.669 --> 23:43.042
WHICH I'M NOT --
I MEAN, AT LEAST NOT YET.

23:43.042 --> 23:44.844
[ Chuckling ] I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE SOMEDAY...

23:44.844 --> 23:45.965
OKAY.

23:45.965 --> 23:48.347
AND I'M GONNA
SHUT UP NOW.

23:48.347 --> 23:51.050
YOU'RE CUTE
WHEN YOU'RE NERVOUS.

23:51.050 --> 23:55.014
[ CHUCKLES ] THEN I MUST BE
THE CUTEST GUY YOU'VE EVER SEEN.

23:56.105 --> 24:00.149
WELL, AS IT HAPPENS,
I ALSO LIKE YOU...

24:00.149 --> 24:01.561
A LOT.

24:01.561 --> 24:04.614
AND I CAN'T THINK OF A BETTER
WAY TO SPEND MY VACATION DAYS

24:04.614 --> 24:06.906
THAN RELAXING ON A BEACH
WITH YOU.

24:06.906 --> 24:09.068
[ SIGHS ]

24:09.068 --> 24:11.120
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]
 [ POPS LIPS ]

24:11.120 --> 24:14.033
AW. WORK.
I GOT TO GO.

24:18.748 --> 24:20.339
OH.

24:20.339 --> 24:23.342
THERE IS ONE CAVEAT,
THOUGH.

24:23.342 --> 24:25.845
I'M MORE
OF A TEQUILA GUY.

24:25.845 --> 24:29.889
BUT I'M CONFIDENT WE CAN WORK
PAST OUR DIFFERENCES.

24:31.180 --> 24:33.182
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:36.055 --> 24:38.057
[ SIGHS ]

24:40.399 --> 24:41.811
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:58.377 --> 25:00.209
YOU WORRIED
ABOUT YOUR DAD?

25:00.209 --> 25:02.792
OF COURSE I'M NOT.
 GOOD.

25:02.792 --> 25:06.505
BECAUSE WE NEED TO FOCUS ON YOU
FOR THE MOMENT.

25:06.505 --> 25:07.837
[ SIGHS ]

25:07.837 --> 25:10.429
DO YOU REALLY THINK I BLEW UP
MY HOUSE TO KILL VICTORIA?

25:10.429 --> 25:11.891
WELL, THERE WAS CERTAINLY
NO LOVE LOST

25:11.891 --> 25:13.302
BETWEEN THE TWO OF YOU,
AND IT'S PRETTY CLEAR

25:13.302 --> 25:15.184
THAT SOMEONE OVERPOWERED
HER IN HER PENTHOUSE.

25:15.184 --> 25:16.596
AND WHEN WOULD
I HAVE DONE THAT?

25:16.596 --> 25:17.977
THE LAST PERSON TO SEE HER
WAS MS. LeMARCHAL

25:17.977 --> 25:20.810
EARLY IN THE EVENING,
WHICH GIVES YOU TIME.

25:20.810 --> 25:22.642
AND IF NOT YOU, I'M SURE ONE
OF YOUR BAND OF MERRY MEN

25:22.642 --> 25:24.233
COULD HAVE TAKEN CARE
OF IT,

25:24.233 --> 25:26.105
MUCH LIKE YOU ALL COVERED UP
DANIEL'S DEATH.

25:27.486 --> 25:29.819
SO, WHERE WERE YOU AROUND 8:00
THE NIGHT OF THE EXPLOSION?

25:29.819 --> 25:33.242
I WAS WITH YOU
AT MY HOUSE.

25:33.242 --> 25:36.035
AND AFTER THAT?
 YOU KNOW WHERE I WAS.

25:36.035 --> 25:37.867
ARE YOU REALLY GONNA
MAKE THIS PERSONAL?

25:37.867 --> 25:39.208
THE SOONER YOU ANSWER
THE QUESTION,

25:39.208 --> 25:40.419
THE SOONER
WE CAN MOVE ON.

25:40.419 --> 25:43.583
I WENT TO THE AIRPORT.

25:43.583 --> 25:44.874
AND DID YOU CATCH JACK?

25:44.874 --> 25:46.005
IS THAT RELEVANT?

25:46.005 --> 25:47.627
IT IS
IF HE'S YOUR ALIBI.

25:47.627 --> 25:49.629
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

25:49.629 --> 25:53.012
I MISSED HIM.
HIS PLANE HAD ALREADY TAKEN OFF.

25:53.012 --> 25:54.223
SO, NO ONE CAN
ACTUALLY CORROBORATE

25:54.223 --> 25:55.434
THAT YOU WENT
TO THE AIRPORT.

25:59.308 --> 26:02.602
[ GROANS ] THIS IS
GONNA BE HARD TO BELIEVE.

26:02.602 --> 26:05.394
UM...
[ CHUCKLES ]

26:07.236 --> 26:09.448
MASON TREADWELL CAN.

26:09.448 --> 26:13.032
THE MASON TREADWELL WHO DIED
IN PRISON LAST YEAR?

26:14.363 --> 26:17.076
SO, A CORPSE IS YOUR ALIBI IN
THE MURDER OF YOUR SWORN ENEMY?

26:17.076 --> 26:20.079
[ SCOFFS ]
 NO, LOOK, HE SHOWED UP
AT THE AIRPORT.

26:20.079 --> 26:22.962
BELIEVE ME, I WAS JUST
AS STUNNED AS YOU ARE.

26:22.962 --> 26:24.543
[ SIGHS ]

26:24.543 --> 26:27.206
I'LL CALL HIM RIGHT NOW.
 PLEASE, KNOCK YOURSELF OUT.

26:27.206 --> 26:28.587
[ CLICKING ]

26:28.587 --> 26:29.799
[ Ringing ]

26:29.799 --> 26:31.210
[ Beeping ]

26:31.210 --> 26:34.053
WOMAN: The number you have
reached has been disconnected.

26:34.053 --> 26:37.176
Please check the number
and dial again.

26:37.176 --> 26:38.978
DEAD MAN DIDN'T PAY
HIS PHONE BILL?

26:38.978 --> 26:41.140
I'LL FIND HIM.

26:41.140 --> 26:42.852
I HOPE YOU DO.

26:42.852 --> 26:44.894
BUT IN THE MEANTIME, DID ANYONE
ELSE SEE YOU WITH MASON?

26:45.685 --> 26:47.897
JIMMY HOFFA?
AMELIA EARHART?

26:47.897 --> 26:49.488
COME ON, BEN. NO.

26:49.488 --> 26:52.111
LOOK, I SAW HIM AGAIN YESTERDAY.
HE'S KEEPING A LOW PROFILE.

26:52.111 --> 26:53.653
WE --
WE TALKED IN MY CAR.

26:53.653 --> 26:55.364
GREAT.
GIVE ME YOUR KEYS.

26:56.495 --> 26:58.287
IF WHAT YOU'RE SAYING IS TRUE,
THEN YOU SHOULD HAVE NO PROBLEM

26:58.287 --> 27:00.159
WITH ME CHECKING YOUR CAR
FOR MASON'S FINGERPRINTS.

27:00.159 --> 27:03.162
FINE.

27:03.162 --> 27:04.583
CAN I GO NOW?

27:04.583 --> 27:07.586
YOU CAN
LEAVE THE ROOM.

27:07.586 --> 27:09.048
JUST DON'T LEAVE TOWN.

27:09.048 --> 27:11.050
[ SCOFFS ]

27:27.026 --> 27:28.978
[ SIGHS ]

27:33.112 --> 27:34.153
WHAT ARE
YOU DOING HERE?

27:34.153 --> 27:35.364
I WAS CALLED BACK
FOR QUESTIONING.

27:35.364 --> 27:37.576
APPARENTLY
WHEN YOU LEAVE TOWN

27:37.576 --> 27:38.988
THE NIGHT SOMEONE
YOU OPENLY HATE IS KILLED,

27:38.988 --> 27:40.239
IT LOOKS
A LITTLE SUSPICIOUS.

27:40.239 --> 27:42.992
[ CHUCKLES ]
 THEY ALREADY TALK TO YOU?

27:42.992 --> 27:46.585
WELL, WHEN SOMEONE YOU OPENLY
HATE DIES IN YOUR HOUSE,

27:46.585 --> 27:49.048
MM, ALSO
A LITTLE SUSPICIOUS.

27:51.340 --> 27:52.752
[ SIGHS ]

27:52.752 --> 27:53.963
JACK, I HAD NOTHING
TO DO WITH IT.

27:53.963 --> 27:56.215
I WASN'T GONNA --
 NO, YOU WERE.

27:56.215 --> 27:57.887
I DON'T BLAME YOU.

27:57.887 --> 28:01.560
[ SIGHS ] IT'S JUST
THIS WHOLE THING, IT'S...

28:01.560 --> 28:03.012
IT'S HARD TO IMAGINE.

28:03.012 --> 28:06.856
YOU KNOW, WHEN I HEARD
ABOUT THE FIRE...

28:10.439 --> 28:13.022
...I'M JUST...
GLAD YOU WEREN'T HOME.

28:13.022 --> 28:14.864
WHY DIDN'T
YOU SAY GOODBYE?

28:16.315 --> 28:19.158
MR. PORTER.
THEY'RE READY FOR YOU.

28:21.951 --> 28:23.162
I SHOULD...

28:24.663 --> 28:28.087
JACK.
[ SIGHS ]

28:28.087 --> 28:30.880
COME BY
THE BEACH HOUSE LATER.

28:30.880 --> 28:33.042
PLEASE.
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

28:37.006 --> 28:38.637
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

28:38.637 --> 28:40.049
AS SOON AS
I'M DONE HERE,

28:40.049 --> 28:41.640
I'M ON THE NEXT FLIGHT
BACK TO L.A.

28:45.514 --> 28:47.937
GOODBYE, AMANDA.

28:57.116 --> 28:59.068
Harris: DID YOU FOLLOW UP
ON DAVID CLARKE'S ALIBI?

28:59.068 --> 29:00.569
Yamada:
YEAH, IT CHECKS OUT.

29:00.569 --> 29:03.783
SPOKE TO A DOCTOR WHO CONFIRMED
HE WAS AT SUFFOLK MEMORIAL.

29:11.630 --> 29:15.634
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

29:15.634 --> 29:16.926
HEY.

29:16.926 --> 29:20.299
AND THERE HE IS.

29:20.299 --> 29:22.221
MARGARITA FOR YOU,
SIR.

29:22.221 --> 29:24.223
PIÃA COLADA FOR ME.

29:24.223 --> 29:25.474
[ GLASSES CLINK ]
 TO OUR DIFFERENCES.

29:27.306 --> 29:30.309
TOO MUCH SALT.
I SHOULD HAVE ASKED.

29:30.309 --> 29:33.732
IT'S NOT THAT.
IT'S JUST...

29:33.732 --> 29:35.734
I CAN'T GO ON A TRIP
WITH YOU.

29:37.156 --> 29:39.778
BECAUSE THE DRINKS
ARE SO GOOD HERE,

29:39.778 --> 29:41.570
WHY LEAVE THE BEACH CLUB?
[ CHUCKLES ]

29:41.570 --> 29:44.904
UM...
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

29:44.904 --> 29:47.706
A FEW MONTHS AGO,

29:47.706 --> 29:49.909
I STARTED
ADOPTION PROCEEDINGS

29:49.909 --> 29:52.001
THROUGH
THE FOSTER-CARE SYSTEM.

29:52.001 --> 29:55.214
I WAS TOLD IT COULD TAKE MONTHS,
MAYBE EVEN YEARS,

29:55.214 --> 29:57.006
WHICH IS WHY
I HADN'T TOLD YOU YET

29:57.006 --> 29:59.008
AND WHY I THOUGHT
I COULD GO ON VACATION.

29:59.008 --> 30:02.631
BUT...

30:02.631 --> 30:05.344
I FOUND OUT TODAY
I'M GETTING A BABY.

30:07.186 --> 30:11.140
[ EXHALES DEEPLY ]
WOW.

30:11.140 --> 30:14.353
THAT'S EXCITING.
I-I MEAN, CONGRATULATIONS.

30:14.353 --> 30:17.026
THANK YOU.
 SOON?

30:17.026 --> 30:19.608
YEAH.
LIKE...IN TWO DAYS.

30:19.608 --> 30:22.491
I HAVE SO MUCH TO DO, I DON'T
EVEN KNOW WHERE TO START.

30:22.491 --> 30:25.905
OKAY, UM...
WE'RE NOT LEAVING TOWN.

30:25.905 --> 30:27.496
WE'LL DRIVE
INTO THE CITY,

30:27.496 --> 30:33.082
AND WE WILL STOCK UP ON ALL
THE SWAG A SINGLE DAD NEEDS.

30:36.715 --> 30:40.299
THAT'S WHAT I NEED TO TALK
TO YOU ABOUT, NOLAN.

30:40.299 --> 30:45.344
THE THING THIS SINGLE DAD NEEDS
IS TO BE SINGLE.

30:47.596 --> 30:53.182
I WOULD LOVE FOR US TO WORK,
BUT BECOMING A DAD...

30:54.813 --> 30:56.395
...I'VE WANTED THIS
FOR A LONG TIME.

30:56.395 --> 31:01.110
AND WHILE IT BOTH EXCITES ME
AND TERRIFIES ME,

31:01.110 --> 31:03.282
IT'S SOMETHING I KNOW
I NEED TO GIVE 100% TO,

31:03.282 --> 31:04.443
AND, IN DOING SO,

31:04.443 --> 31:05.654
OUR RELATIONSHIP WOULD
GET SHORT-CHANGED,

31:05.654 --> 31:07.446
YOU WILL BE
SHORT-CHANGED.

31:07.446 --> 31:09.248
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

31:09.248 --> 31:12.251
OKAY, UM...

31:12.251 --> 31:13.872
TONY...

31:13.872 --> 31:17.086
[ SIGHS ]
...DESPITE APPEARANCES...

31:17.086 --> 31:20.459
I CAN BE
PRETTY LOW-MAINTENANCE.

31:20.459 --> 31:21.961
I PROMISE.

31:26.305 --> 31:29.138
I'M SORRY, NOLAN.

31:30.469 --> 31:33.472
IT WOULDN'T BE FAIR TO YOU
OR TO ME OR TO MY LITTLE BOY.

31:41.610 --> 31:44.823
WELL, I WISH I'D MET YOU
A YEAR AGO.

31:47.236 --> 31:50.909
ME TOO.

31:55.204 --> 31:58.207
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

32:00.749 --> 32:02.541
GOODBYE, NOLAN.

32:17.556 --> 32:19.148
BYE.

32:22.651 --> 32:24.063
THE CAR PICKED US UP
AROUND 7:00.

32:24.063 --> 32:25.654
BY 8:30,
WE WERE IN THE AIR.

32:25.654 --> 32:27.236
OKAY, I'M GONNA NEED
THE NAME OF THE CAR SERVICE

32:27.236 --> 32:30.029
AND THAT PLANE'S
TAIL NUMBER.

32:30.029 --> 32:33.072
I GET THAT THE TIMING
OF MY DEPARTURE SEEMS CURIOUS.

32:33.072 --> 32:35.074
A GUY LIVES HERE
HIS WHOLE LIFE.

32:35.074 --> 32:36.705
SPUR OF THE MOMENT,
MOVES TO CALIFORNIA

32:36.705 --> 32:39.078
MINUTES BEFORE GRAYSON MANOR
GOES UP IN FLAMES.

32:39.078 --> 32:40.789
YEAH.

32:40.789 --> 32:44.003
I COULD HAVE ANSWERED
THESE QUESTIONS OVER THE PHONE.

32:44.003 --> 32:46.045
BUT WE BOTH KNOW
THOSE CALLS ARE RECORDED.

32:47.676 --> 32:49.678
SO, WHAT DID YOU
REALLY WANT TO ASK ME?

32:55.594 --> 32:57.186
DID YOU HELP HER?

32:59.098 --> 33:01.190
OF COURSE NOT.

33:01.190 --> 33:02.441
LOOK, I'M DOING YOU A FAVOR
BY KEEPING THIS OFF THE RECORD

33:02.441 --> 33:03.732
BECAUSE YOU AND I
BOTH KNOW

33:03.732 --> 33:06.735
THAT YOU HAVE HELPED EMILY
COVER UP THINGS IN THE PAST.

33:06.735 --> 33:08.487
I NEED YOU
TO BE HONEST WITH ME HERE.

33:10.199 --> 33:12.371
WELL,
THEN LET ME BE CLEAR.

33:12.371 --> 33:15.374
I HAD ABSOLUTELY NOTHING TO DO
WITH VICTORIA GRAYSON'S DEATH.

33:15.374 --> 33:18.417
I WAS WITH MY FAMILY
THE ENTIRE NIGHT.

33:18.417 --> 33:21.540
AND HAS EMILY SAID ANYTHING
TO YOU ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED?

33:21.540 --> 33:23.622
LOOK, THE ONLY TIME
I'VE SPOKEN WITH EMILY RECENTLY

33:23.622 --> 33:25.254
WAS A FEW MINUTES AGO
WHEN SHE ASSURED ME

33:25.254 --> 33:26.755
SHE HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH THIS.

33:26.755 --> 33:30.589
NOW, LET ME ASK YOU A QUESTION
OFF THE RECORD.

33:30.589 --> 33:33.182
ISN'T THIS A CONFLICT
OF INTEREST?

33:33.182 --> 33:34.973
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:34.973 --> 33:37.396
YOU WORKING ON A CASE THAT
INVOLVES YOUR GIRLFRIEND?

33:37.396 --> 33:39.728
YOU DON'T KNOW?

33:40.979 --> 33:42.351
KNOW WHAT?

33:42.351 --> 33:45.023
WE BROKE UP
THE NIGHT YOU LEFT.

33:45.023 --> 33:48.857
SHE RAN TO THE AIRPORT
TO STOP YOU.

33:48.857 --> 33:51.650
YOU WON, PORTER.

33:51.650 --> 33:53.152
SHE CHOSE YOU.

34:03.502 --> 34:07.796
[ SIREN WAILING IN DISTANCE ]

34:11.469 --> 34:13.092
AMANDA.

34:13.092 --> 34:15.094
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

34:15.094 --> 34:19.016
DR. FOGEL,
CHIEF OF ONCOLOGY.

34:19.016 --> 34:22.101
THAT'S WHO CORROBORATED
YOUR STORY THE OTHER NIGHT.

34:24.483 --> 34:26.485
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

34:26.485 --> 34:28.147
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME?

34:31.949 --> 34:36.324
THE OTHER DAY WHEN YOU
CAME BY MY HOUSE

34:36.324 --> 34:38.327
AND TOLD ME
THAT EVERYTHING WAS OVER

34:38.327 --> 34:40.329
AND THAT THERE WERE NO MORE
BATTLES TO BE FOUGHT,

34:40.329 --> 34:42.751
I SAW A LOOK IN YOUR EYE

34:42.751 --> 34:45.543
THAT I HAVEN'T SEEN
SINCE I'VE BEEN BACK,

34:45.543 --> 34:49.467
SINCE...
SINCE YOU WERE A GIRL.

34:49.467 --> 34:54.092
AND I WASN'T ABLE TO
DESTROY THAT.

34:54.092 --> 34:56.514
YOU DON'T HAVE TO
PROTECT ME.

34:56.514 --> 34:59.888
I KNOW I DON'T HAVE TO.
BUT I WANT TO.

35:01.720 --> 35:04.603
LOOK, IT'S A FORM
OF LYMPHOMA.

35:04.603 --> 35:06.605
THE GOOD NEWS IS
THEY GOT IT EARLY,

35:06.605 --> 35:08.277
AND I'M GETTING
CUTTING-EDGE TREATMENT.

35:08.277 --> 35:10.569
EVERYTHING'S
GONNA BE FINE.

35:10.569 --> 35:12.571
[ SIGHS ]

35:15.534 --> 35:18.157
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

35:18.157 --> 35:20.329
OH, YOU KNOW,
I'M OKAY.

35:20.329 --> 35:23.202
TIRED, BUT I'M OKAY.

35:23.202 --> 35:27.206
WELL, BETTER NOW
THAT YOU KNOW.

35:27.206 --> 35:29.127
SORRY
I KEPT IT FROM YOU.

35:29.127 --> 35:33.802
WE'RE IN THIS TOGETHER NOW.
THAT'S ALL THAT MATTERS.

35:33.802 --> 35:35.884
[ CHUCKLES ]
ALL RIGHT.

35:40.469 --> 35:43.262
[ SIGHS ]

35:43.262 --> 35:45.684
WHAT DO YOU SAY
WE HAVE A MOVIE NIGHT?

35:45.684 --> 35:48.477
I'LL GO GET SOME POPCORN, AND,
UH, WE'LL MEET AT THE HOUSE.

35:48.477 --> 35:50.479
SOUNDS PERFECT.

35:57.576 --> 36:00.869
HOW'S IT COMING?

36:00.869 --> 36:03.202
WE ARE JUST ABOUT DONE,
DETECTIVE.

36:03.202 --> 36:06.084
YOU FIND
ANY CLEAN PRINTS?

36:06.084 --> 36:06.995
A BUNCH.

36:06.995 --> 36:08.997
WE'LL RUN THEM THROUGH AFIS,
SEE IF WE GET A HIT.

36:08.997 --> 36:12.501
ALSO, FOUND A FEW STRANDS
OF HAIR WITH FOLLICULAR TAGS.

36:12.501 --> 36:14.092
GREAT.
CHECK EVERYTHING.

36:16.255 --> 36:17.676
Louise: WHAT'S THAT
STAGE OF GRIEF

36:17.676 --> 36:19.468
WHERE YOU WANT TO
THROTTLE SOMEONE?

36:19.468 --> 36:21.220
I CAN'T BE SURE.

36:21.220 --> 36:24.182
I'M STARTING TO FEEL
AS IF THAT'S MY BASELINE.

36:26.014 --> 36:29.067
I FEEL SO HELPLESS.

36:29.067 --> 36:31.650
WE'RE JUST SITTING HERE
LIKE LAME DUCKS

36:31.650 --> 36:34.403
WALLOWING IN OUR GRIEF
WHILE SHE GOES ON WITH HER LIFE.

36:34.403 --> 36:36.365
DID YOU GIVE YOUR STATEMENT
TO THE POLICE?

36:36.365 --> 36:37.776
YES.

36:37.776 --> 36:40.078
I TOLD THEM VICTORIA
FEARED FOR HER SAFETY.

36:40.078 --> 36:42.120
[ SIGHS ]

36:42.120 --> 36:45.284
BUT AMANDA,
SHE'S...SLIPPERY.

36:45.284 --> 36:47.706
SHE DIDN'T EVEN BAT AN EYE
WHEN I ACCUSED HER

36:47.706 --> 36:49.418
OF KILLING VICTORIA,
AND I KNOW SHE DID IT.

36:51.039 --> 36:52.791
I HAVE TO DO SOMETHING.

36:52.791 --> 36:55.043
OH, I'M ONE STEP
AHEAD OF YOU.

36:55.043 --> 36:56.425
HMM.

36:56.425 --> 36:58.006
WHAT IS ALL THIS?

36:58.006 --> 37:01.470
SOMETHING I SHOULD HAVE
DONE WEEKS AGO.

37:01.470 --> 37:03.842
VICTORIA CAME TO ME ASKING
TO USE MY MEDIA OUTLETS

37:03.842 --> 37:08.056
IN HER CASE AGAINST AMANDA,
BUT I REFUSED.

37:08.056 --> 37:10.349
SOMETHING
I WILL ALWAYS REGRET.

37:10.349 --> 37:12.150
MARGAUX.

37:12.150 --> 37:14.523
NOW, THIS WON'T BRING
VICTORIA BACK.

37:14.523 --> 37:17.195
BUT I'LL BE DAMNED
IF I DON'T USE EVERY RESOURCE

37:17.195 --> 37:19.988
AT MY DISPOSAL
TO MAKE THIS RIGHT.

37:29.998 --> 37:32.000
[ KEYS CLATTER ]

37:35.294 --> 37:37.296
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

37:42.220 --> 37:43.141
HELLO?

37:43.141 --> 37:45.143
THE WHEELS OF JUSTICE
MOVE SWIFTLY.

37:45.143 --> 37:48.557
I JUST RECEIVED A NEWS ALERT
THAT MY NAME HAS BEEN CLEARED.

37:48.557 --> 37:50.349
WELL DONE, AMANDA.

37:50.349 --> 37:53.061
I HAVE BEEN CALLING AND CALLING.
WHERE THE HELL ARE YOU?

37:53.061 --> 37:56.024
OH, JUST FOLLOWING ORDERS.
STAYING OUT OF SIGHT.

37:56.024 --> 37:58.236
REMEMBER,
INNOCENCE ASIDE,

37:58.236 --> 38:01.109
IN THE EYES OF THE WORLD,
I'M STILL SIX FEET UNDER.

38:01.109 --> 38:02.401
Well,
I'm gonna need to

38:02.401 --> 38:04.112
RESURRECT YOU
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE.

38:04.112 --> 38:06.074
YOU'RE MY ALIBI
THE NIGHT VICTORIA DIED.

38:06.074 --> 38:09.077
OOH. TOUGH BREAK.

38:09.077 --> 38:11.079
'CAUSE I HAVE NO INTENTION
OF SEEING YOU AGAIN.

38:11.079 --> 38:12.210
EVER.

38:12.210 --> 38:13.372
Consider it payback

38:13.372 --> 38:15.173
for all the hell
you put me through.

38:15.173 --> 38:19.418
HOW DOES IT FEEL TO HAVE
THE LOUBOUTIN ON THE OTHER FOOT?

38:19.418 --> 38:21.009
I KNOW YOU, MASON.

38:21.009 --> 38:23.051
SOONER OR LATER,
YOU WILL GET TIRED

38:23.051 --> 38:24.633
OF WHATEVER ROCK
YOU'RE LIVING UNDER

38:24.633 --> 38:26.184
AND YOUR EGO WON'T
BE ABLE TO RESIST THE URGE

38:26.184 --> 38:29.057
TO ANNOUNCE YOUR GLORIOUS RETURN
TO THE LIVING.

38:29.057 --> 38:30.639
DON'T HOLD YOUR BREATH,
UNLESS YOU HAVE

38:30.639 --> 38:33.021
A VICTORIA GRAYSON-LEVEL
DEATH WISH, THAT IS.

38:33.021 --> 38:38.236
And speaking
of our dearly departed,

38:38.236 --> 38:41.239
VICTORIA HAD ONE FINAL REQUEST
BEFORE KILLING HERSELF.

38:41.239 --> 38:43.442
SHE ASKED ME TO PASS ALONG
A MESSAGE TO YOU.

38:43.442 --> 38:45.654
That's right.

38:45.654 --> 38:49.748
After your scintillating
TV tell-all,

38:49.748 --> 38:51.119
I REACHED OUT
TO THE ONE PERSON

38:51.119 --> 38:54.122
WHO'D BEEN SCREWED
HARDER THAN ME.

38:54.122 --> 38:56.955
SEE YOU NEVER, AMANDA.

38:56.955 --> 39:00.298
[ BEEP ]

39:00.298 --> 39:01.960
[ CELLPHONE CHIMES ]

39:01.960 --> 39:02.961
[ CLICK ]

39:02.961 --> 39:04.342
Victoria: HELLO, AMANDA.

39:04.342 --> 39:07.095
I'M SENDING YOU THIS MESSAGE

39:07.095 --> 39:10.178
TO TELL YOU THAT I'M ENDING
YOUR GAME OF REVENGE.

39:10.178 --> 39:13.812
BY THE TIME YOU RECEIVE THIS,

39:13.812 --> 39:16.395
I'LL NO LONGER
BE AMONG THE LIVING.

39:16.395 --> 39:19.398
BUT I WOULD BE REMISS
IF I DIDN'T THANK YOU

39:19.398 --> 39:22.981
FOR THAT BRILLIANT IDEA I FOUND
ON THAT FLASH DRIVE OF YOURS.

39:22.981 --> 39:25.824
JUST AS YOU WERE PLANNING
ON MAKING IT APPEAR

39:25.824 --> 39:30.038
AS IF I HAD MURDERED YOU
ON YOUR FARCICAL WEDDING NIGHT,

39:30.038 --> 39:32.621
I'M GOING TO MAKE IT APPEAR

39:32.621 --> 39:34.873
AS IF YOU MURDERED ME
IN YOUR OWN HOME.

39:34.873 --> 39:36.875
THE ONLY DIFFERENCE --

39:36.875 --> 39:39.418
YOU NEVER ACTUALLY HAD THE GUTS
TO KILL YOURSELF.

39:39.418 --> 39:40.999
BUT I DO.

39:40.999 --> 39:42.841
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:42.841 --> 39:45.213
SO I SUPPOSE THAT MAKES ME
THE VICTOR IN OUR LITTLE GAME,

39:45.213 --> 39:47.265
BUT THEN WHO'S KEEPING SCORE?

39:47.265 --> 39:50.388
ENJOY YOUR LIFE IN PRISON,
MY DEAR.

39:50.388 --> 39:54.392
[ SIRENS WAILING ]
 MAY YOU SUFFER GREATLY.

39:54.392 --> 39:56.394
[ TIRES SCREECH ]
 [ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

39:56.394 --> 39:59.397
[ DOOR OPENS ]
 Ben: HOLD IT RIGHT THERE.

39:59.397 --> 40:01.109
BEN, LISTEN TO ME.
 AMANDA CLARKE,
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST

40:01.109 --> 40:02.280
FOR THE MURDER
OF VICTORIA GRAYSON.

40:02.280 --> 40:04.322
VICTORIA SET ME UP.
WE JUST HAVE TO FIND
MASON TREADWELL.

40:04.322 --> 40:05.984
THE MASON TREADWELL
YOU CLAIM WAS IN YOUR CAR?

40:05.984 --> 40:08.987
HIS FINGERPRINTS
WERE NOWHERE TO BE FOUND.
 THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

